Common Commands for Virtual Environments
Task	--> Command
Create a virtual environment --> 	python3 -m venv myenv
Activate on Linux/macOS --> 	source myenv/bin/activate
Activate on Windows --> 	myenv\Scripts\activate
Deactivate --> 	deactivate
Install libraries -->	pip install <library_name>
List installed libraries-->	pip list
Delete the virtual environment -->	rm -rf myenv
